Disk World creator help
set_display_subheadings

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_display_subheadings -  This method allows you to switch the subheadings ("Alcoholic Beverages", "Meals", etc) that appear above different types of items on and off.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_display_subheadings(int value)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^value%^RESET%^ - set to 1 to display subheadings or 0 to remove them
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/inherit/pub.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method allows you to switch the subheadings ("Alcoholic Beverages",
"Meals", etc) that appear above different types of items on and off.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_display_subheadings(), set_menu_subheadings(), query_menu_subheadings()

.EP

